tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  52,15,"E ko mbilewu woni ɗee lepte ɗe sutiɗon? Kaa hara on alaa e yi'ude?"
  52,20,"Hara ko on soɓɓindiiɓe e hoore danɗe cuɗinaaɗe weertindiraa. Men resini ɓe kadi rewɓe yooɗa giteeɓe."
  52,23,"Hiɓe jaaondira ka nder Aljanna ton : ñedduɗe ɗe jillaa njaram wa'uɗam wa njaramji goo aduna; woni ko siwrinta adda cona-cana maa ko sabimbinta bakkaatu."